@startuml
title CMDB Integral - Flujo MVC
actor Usuario
boundary "Vista PHP" as View
control "Controller" as Controller
control "Core\nAuth/CSRF/Validator" as Core
entity "Model PDO" as Model
database "MySQL" as DB

Usuario -> View : envia formulario o abre ruta
View -> Controller : HTTP GET/POST
Controller -> Core : autoriza, valida CSRF, sanea
Controller -> Model : ejecuta caso de uso
Model -> DB : consultas preparadas
DB --> Model : filas
Model --> Controller : datos
Controller -> View : renderiza o redirige
View --> Usuario : HTML / Excel / SVG
@enduml
